    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evil stirs. Not only does a deadly plague ravage the land, consuming entire villages, but rumours abound that the long-forgotten old gods including Despater, the God of Death, have awakened from slumber. Join Betha, a mysterious girl with a powerful secret, and the survivors of Tadec on a desperate quest to uncover the truth and destroy the source of the blight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206020/extras/de030c3f116eacc9cc62ac55fb656779.poster.avif?t=1761678791\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206020/extras/de030c3f116eacc9cc62ac55fb656779.webm?t=1761678791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206020/extras/de030c3f116eacc9cc62ac55fb656779.mp4?t=1761678791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse a rich medieval fantasy world across 32 branching scenarios and confront the evil that schemes in the shadows. The choices you make – who you choose to ally with, who you leave behind, and what you’re willing to sacrifice – will shape the fate of the world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206020/extras/615bb7c9ef3baa7f06198f03f9fc9dd1.poster.avif?t=1761678791\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206020/extras/615bb7c9ef3baa7f06198f03f9fc9dd1.webm?t=1761678791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206020/extras/615bb7c9ef3baa7f06198f03f9fc9dd1.mp4?t=1761678791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactical turn-based combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maneuver your team, choose your actions wisely, and outwit your enemies using terrain, timing, and tactical insight. Classic party-based strategy: Form your party from a diverse array of warriors, each with their unique skills, strengths, and stories.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Difficult Decisions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every encounter presents the risk of character perma-death. When a party member dies, will you forge ahead with a replacement, or reload and try again? Who will you recruit and who will you leave behind?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A rich, driving story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An epic narrative inspired by Celtic mythology and medieval folklore. Rich world-building, character-driven storytelling, and branching paths that reflect your decisions ensure each playthrough feels fresh.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic character progression</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customise your party with new skills and equipment earned through battle. Develop your heroes into hardened veterans.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactical multiplayer battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your own party, test your skills, and go join your friends in intense skirmishes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An immersive, replayable campaign</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With branching choices, region-specific recruits, and difficult decisions ahead, no two journeys are ever the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206020/extras/3ed8cbd9ae5024396209da752d245b68.poster.avif?t=1761678791\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206020/extras/3ed8cbd9ae5024396209da752d245b68.webm?t=1761678791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206020/extras/3ed8cbd9ae5024396209da752d245b68.mp4?t=1761678791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
